article_title: Some area residents will see higher premiums for ACA health insurance plans
article_text:
Affordable Care Act open enrollment starts Sunday

Premiums for benchmark silver plan will go up 20.1 percent in area

Residents of Johnson and Wyandotte counties will choose from just two plan providers

article_metadata.description: Premiums will go up substantially next year for some Kansas City area residents enrolled in health insurance plans through the Affordable Care Act’s marketplace.
